  "raw_content": "Decoder使用3UMA方案测试\n一、背景\n原来的的方案时UNU，现在ZTE需要尝试使用3UMA的方案，现在改动 S8的代码来验证性能。\n二、测试\n使用llama2-7B的shape进行测试。\n\n\n\n\nUNU\n\n\n\nUUU\n\n\n\n（B, H, K, W)\n\n（1， 1， 4096， 4096）\n\n（1， 1， 11008， 4096）\n\n（1， 1， 4096， 4096）\n\n（1， 1， 11008， 4096）\n\nperSpc\n\n(1, 1, 4096, 256)\n\n(1, 1, 11008, 256)\n\n(1, 1, 4096, 256)\n\n(1, 1, 11008, 256)\n\nreload_a_gib\n\n1\n\n1\n\n1\n\n1\n\nreload_b_gib\n\n1\n\n1\n\n1\n\n1\n\nload_a_hbm_to_gib\n\n64 x 4096 x 2 / 60 = 8,738\n\n64 * 11008 x 2 / 60 = 23,483\n\n64 x 4096 x 2 / 60 = 8,738\n\n64 * 11008 x 2 / 60 = 23,483\n\nload_b_hbm_to_gib\n\n4096 x 256 x 1 / 40 = 26,214\n\n11008 * 256 * 1 / 40 = 70,451\n\n4096 x 256 x 1 / 30 =34952\n\n11008 * 256 * 1 / 30 = 93934\n\nmma\n\n64 * 4096 * 256 / 16384 = 4096\n\n64 * 11008 * 256 / 16384 = 11,008\n\n64 * 4096 * 256 / 16384 = 4096\n\n64 * 11008 * 256 / 16384 = 11,008\n\nwrite_l2\n\n64 * 256 * (4096 / 2048) / 256 = 128\n\n64 * 256 * (4096 / 2048) / 256 = 128\n\n64 * 256 * (4096 / 2048) / 256 = 128\n\n64 * 256 * (4096 / 2048) / 256 = 128\n\ntypecast\n\n64 * 256 * 2 / 30 = 1092\n\n64 * 256 * 2 / 30 = 1092\n\n64 * 256 * 2 / 30 = 1092\n\n64 * 256 * 2 / 30 = 1092\n\nresult\n\nmax(  Load_A_From_HBM_To_GIB + Load_B_From_HBM_To_GIB ,  Gemm ,  Acc_Write_C )  + typecast_Write_C\n= max( 8,738 + 26,214, 4096, 128) + 1092\n= 36,044\n\nmax(23483+70451, 11008,, 128) + 1092\n=  95,026\n\n=max( 8,738 + 34952, 4096, 128) + 1092\n= 44782\n\nmax(23483+93934, 11008,, 128) + 1092\n=  118509\n\n下降比例 %\n\n\n\n\n\n24.24%\n\n24.71%\n实际测试：\n\n\nshape\n\nUNU\n\n3UMA\n\n下降比例\n\nUNU\n\n3UMA\n\n(1, 1, 4096, 4096)\n\n41887\n\n65240\n\n55.75%\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-14-40.png\n\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-15-1.png\n\n\n(1, 1, 11008, 4096)\n\n92524\n\n138860\n\n33.36%\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-13-51.png\n\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-14-11.png\n\n\n(1, 1, 8192, 8192)\n\n127495\n\n230575\n\n80.85%\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-13-19.png\n\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-12-58.png\n\n\n(1, 1, 7168, 8192)\n\n99803\n\n190776\n\n91.1%\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-11-57.png\n\n\nimage2024-5-16_17-11-40.png\n\n\n",
